Pre-fix (verified with the unmodified deploy at gh-pages):
- Same URL → empty OUTPUT panel.
- Network panel showed only OPTIONS to https://api.polst.app
  (prod default) returning CORS 503. The render's REST origin came
  from the widget global, which is bundled in a separate esm.sh
  module realm from `@polst-web/sdk`'s configureOrigins re-export,
  so writes to that global can't reach the render's REST client.

Fix is a 4-line edit in docs/sdk/sdk.js: pass `apiOrigin` to each
renderPolst / renderCampaign / renderBrandFeed call. No `--provenance`
issue here; this is the polst-embedding repo, separate publish path.
